{"tid":391760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"約40人到教育大學示威不滿諷刺蔡若蓮大字報","createTime":"2017-09-08T04:35:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-08T04:36:08.000Z","uid":48093,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"82c176addef8f54456166d942ac28b74a8e3e059","tid":391760,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T04:35:04.000Z","msg":"教育局副局長蔡若蓮長子昨日墮樓身亡，有人於教育大學民主牆張貼諷刺字句。<br />\n<br />\n來自不同團體約40人到教育大學示威，表達不滿，又高呼「落井下石 」、「道德淪喪」等口號。<br />\n<br />\n團體要求張貼字句的人，公開道歉，為自己的行為負責。團體又認為，如教大校方證實張貼字句人是該校學生，應按照程序處罰。"},{"pid":"7a6acebdb4f89b6f2fc993bd63364ea3d673f236","tid":391760,"uid":141804,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T04:35:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"314ed78c0eec1d663a17c1bfef82803a35ed98db","tid":391760,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-08T04:36:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">隨時根本係自己人做賊喊捉賊既反擊大龍鳳囉！！！</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://holland.pk/a0txqc21\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fa0txqc21&h=88bc0383&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">兇宅跌一半：正皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette2.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/1/1c/Chow200.jpg/revision/latest/thumbnail-down/width/352/height/288?cb=20100325123623\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette2.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F1%2F1c%2FChow200.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%2Fthumbnail-down%2Fwidth%2F352%2Fheight%2F288%3Fcb%3D20100325123623&h=97e54f